metadata.symbol: The key to your digital assets
metadata.description:
The BARRRY Spacehsip Captain Membership gives you the following superpower:

  • Alpha Access to the BARRRY App
  • Lifetime Access to the BARRRY App
  • Access to limited exclusive physical Swag (worldwide free delivery)
  • Eligible for all surprise Barrry Airdrops (unique NFT’s and BRY token)
  • Beeing part of “The Deck”: You will be able to participate actively on the product roadmap in an exclusive circle.
  • Breeding of 10 1-Year-Memberships per year
